item.title: Spittin’ Chiclets Episode 534: Featuring Jake Middleton, Jay Pandolfo & a Mystery Detective
item.description: On Episode 534 of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Minnesota Wild Defenseman Jake Middleton to talk about his years in San Jose, going from laying brick to playing in the NHL and the surprise trade to Minnesota that he now calls come. Later on the boys catch up with Boston University head Coach Jay Pandolfo to talk about his view on the state of college hockey, the process to develop players, and tons of old hockey stories...
